snippet.title: Amber Studio
snippet.description:
Amber is a global independent game development agency based in Bucharest, Botosani, San Francisco, Los Angeles, Guadalajara & Montreal, offering premium software development services for creative industries. 
Our vision is to be the game development agency of choice for partners and players everywhere. We aim to achieve this by assembling the industry's leading talent in production, engineering, design, art and data science into our multi-track studio and service teams, in order to deliver a reference solution for publishers and developers.
